FBIS3-52158 "drnes001_r_94005" FBIS-NES-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 India Rao Refuses Finance Minister's Resignation BK3112130893 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1230 GMT 31 Dec 93 BK3112130893 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The prime minister has refused to accept the resignation of the finance minister, Dr. Manmohan Singh. This was stated by the official spokesman in New Delhi today. The prime minister, in a letter to Dr. Singh, said taking all factors into consideration, including the enormous agenda of work, it would not be appropriate for him to resign.
